 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
 4. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the security-guard##1
 8. the accountant is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the accountant##1
11. the writer is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
12. the teacher is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the writer##3
14. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
15. the pilot is in an even position##4
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
17. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
18. the person driving the helicopter is the social-worker##1
19. the pilot is on the left of the lawyer##1
20. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |       3       |     4      |   5    |       6        |   7    |
